<section class="border-b border-[#dce5da] py-16">
    <div class="section-shell grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.92fr] lg:items-center">
        <div>
            <p class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-normal text-[#0f766e]">Messenger sharing</p>
            <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-normal text-[#13201d] md:text-4xl">Better than sending raw files in chat</h2>
            <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-[#52625d]">
                When you need to send a private file through Telegram, Slack, Discord, or email, SecShare lets you share an encrypted temporary link instead of uploading the original file directly to the messenger.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-5 rounded-lg border border-[#ead7a7] bg-[#fff8e6] p-4 text-sm leading-6 text-[#6d5521]">
